    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s basically in showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent anywhere! It drives like a dream and has been babied since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. I've kept it tucked away in the garage and it's ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
