      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a peerless E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This example boasts a comprehensive mechanical pedigree, including a proactive double-VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement for total peace of mind. The drivetrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec helical limited-slip differential. The chassis has been professionally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points and upgraded with Bilstein B16 PSS10 adjustable coilovers for superior lateral grip and precise transient response. The exterior maintains a mirror-like finish with zero oxidation, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple with impeccable bolsters. This is a turnkey, high-performance specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
