    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and features a flawless Guards Red exterior protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the black leather interior remains in a pristine state, still carrying that new-car scent with absolutely no wear on the seat bolsters, steering wheel, or touchpoints. With only 12,000 miles on the odometer, it has been serviced exclusively at Porsche authorized centers, with a full binder of service records available for your review. The car sits on brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires and has never seen rain, snow, or track use. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern performance icon that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership floor. Zero scratches, zero dents, and a completely clean history for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
